(40, 13, 21, 43, 15, 5, 7, 'dureth for a while', 'Connection of Abiding and Endurance', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of enduring faith. Matthew highlights the danger of being offended during tribulation, while John stresses the necessity of abiding in Christ to bear fruit.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
